io.nebulas.account

Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.nebulas.account.Account

  • public class Account
extends java.lang.Object
    The Account class.

    Account only contains account address and keyPath info.

    • Address is the object that contains address info for this account
    • KeyPath is the local file path where the account wallet json file is stored.
    See Also:
    Address
